quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,1,"Alif Lam Ra, lawa ngamavesi encwadi ecacile"
  12,2,Ngempela thina sayembula iQur’an (ngolimi) lwesi-Arab ukuze mhlawumbe niqonde
  12,3,"Thina sikuxoxela izindaba ezimnandi ngokwedlulele ngesikwembulile kuwena, lena iQur’an yize noma ngaphambilini kwayo wawungomunye wabanganakile"
  12,4,"Khumbula ngenkathi uJosefa ethi kuyise, “Oh baba wami! ngempela mina ngibone (ephuphweni) izinkanyezi eziyishumi nanye nelanga nenyanga ngizibone zingikhothamela.”"
  12,5,"(Uyise) wathi, “Oh ndodana yami! ungabaxoxeli abafowenu iphupho lakho hleze bakudalele icebo ngempela usathane uyisitha somuntu esigqamile”"
  12,6,Futhi kanjalo iNkosi yakho iyakukhetha futhi ikufundisa ukuchazwa kwamaphupho futhi iphelelise ububele bayo phezu kwakho kanye nasemndenini kaJakobe njengoba yawuphelelisa phezu kwabazali bakho bobabili ngaphambi kuka-Abraham no-Isaka ngempela iNkosi yakho iyisazi inobuhlakani